                  </para>
                </label-para>
                <label-para skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                  <para>
                    <text>they were made by an existing local authority:</text>
                  </para>
                </label-para>
                <label-para skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">c</label>
                  <para>
                    <text>they are in force at the close of 31 October 2010.</text>
                  </para>
                </label-para>
              </para>
            </subprov>
            <subprov skeleton="no">
              <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">2</label>
              <para>
                <text>On and from 1 November 2010 the bylaws are deemed to have been made by the Auckland Council.</text>
              </para>
            </subprov>
            <subprov skeleton="no">
              <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">3</label>
              <para>
                <text>Each bylaw remains in force in the area to which it applied at the close of 31 October 2010 until<struckoutwords amend.level1="struckout-majority"> one of the following occurs:</struckoutwords><insertwords amend.level1="insert-majority"> 31 October 2015, when it is revoked, unless before that date—</insertwords></text>
                <label-para skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
